  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLocated by Green Island Lake in Foshan City, Guangdong, China, the \u003cstrong\u003eBoundless Residence\u003c/strong\u003e, designed by \u003cstrong\u003ec.dd\u003c/strong\u003e, embodies the philosophy of “Limited yet Boundless.” The design seeks to merge the tranquility of nature with modern living spaces, creating an environment where physical comfort and spiritual rejuvenation coexist. \u003cspan\u003eRather than adhering to the rigid boundaries of traditional homes, c.dd adopted a fluid, open-plan layout that allows for an uninterrupted flow between different spaces. The design eliminates physical barriers, ensuring that each area – from the entrance to the living room, dining room, kitchen, and study – blends seamlessly with the next. This open layout transforms the home from a static space into a dynamic, ever-evolving environment that mirrors the fluidity of life itself.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/the-boundless-residence-merges-natures-with-modern-living-spaces/boundess-residence-guangdong-china-lake-cdd-2/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-556618\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-2-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A modern living room featuring a large TV, a white sectional sofa, a yellow armchair, and a geometric rug. The room has wooden flooring and is illuminated by natural light through sheer curtains.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-2-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-2-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09