es or sharp corners in nature. The straight line belongs to men, the curved line belongs to God.” In keeping with this philosophy, c.dd incorporated gentle, flowing curves throughout the design, from the rounded ceilings to the soft edges of the furnishings. This approach creates a warm, inviting environment that echoes the organic forms found in nature, softening the overall aesthetic of the home.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/the-boundless-residence-merges-natures-with-modern-living-spaces/boundess-residence-guangdong-china-lake-cdd-4/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-556620\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-4-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"A modern living room features a white sofa with two black coffee tables, a vase with a sprig of greenery, and a minimalist wall with soft lighting. Blue and white geometric rug on the floor.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-4-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-4-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-4-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-4-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-4.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe curves are complemented by concealed, ambient lighting, which enhances the serene atmosphere of the space. Gentle illumination pours from the curved ceilings, bathing the interiors in soft light that subtly shifts with the time of day, creating a calming visual experience that fosters a sense of peace. The use of natural materials – wood, stone, and fabric – reinforces the connection to the surrounding landscape, blending the interior spaces with the natural environment outside.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/the-boundless-residence-merges-natures-with-modern-living-spaces/boundess-residence-guangdong-china-lake-cdd-5/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-556621\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-5-810x455.jpg\" alt=\"A modern living room with a large TV mounted on a wall, a yellow chair, two round tables, and a potted plant. The room features wooden flooring and large windows with sheer curtains.\" width=\"810\" height=\"455\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-5-810x455.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-5-800x449.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-5-768x431.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-5-600x337.jpg 600w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-5.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/the-boundless-residence-merges-natures-with-modern-living-spaces/boundess-residence-guangdong-china-lake-cdd-6/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-556622\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-6-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"A modern living space featuring a large flat-screen TV mounted on a wall, a yellow contemporary chair, a small side table, and a seating area with a wooden dining table visible in the background.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boun