w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-9-768x497.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-9.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/the-boundless-residence-merges-natures-with-modern-living-spaces/boundess-residence-guangdong-china-lake-cdd-10/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-556626\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-10-810x456.jpg\" alt=\"A modern living room with a yellow sofa, white walls, and wooden flooring. A potted plant is in the foreground, and the space is decorated with contemporary lighting fixtures and minimalist furniture.\" width=\"810\" height=\"456\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-10-810x456.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-10-800x451.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-10-768x433.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-10-600x337.jpg 600w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-10.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/the-boundless-residence-merges-natures-with-modern-living-spaces/boundess-residence-guangdong-china-lake-cdd-11/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-556627\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-11-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Modern interior featuring a curved wall with a circular window, wooden bench, and view of an open-plan l