mg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-21-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Modern hotel room with a sleek desk setup featuring a laptop, lamp, and chair. The room includes a bed, large window with curtains, and wooden flooring.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-21-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-21-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-21-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-21.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/the-boundless-residence-merges-natures-with-modern-living-spaces/boundess-residence-guangdong-china-lake-cdd-22/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-556638\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-22-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A modern hallway features wooden walls and floor, a built-in desk with a chair, and a wardrobe with glass doors on the right side.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-22-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-22-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-22-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-22.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/the-boundless-residence-merges-natures-with-modern-living-spaces/boundess-residence-guangdong-china-lake-cdd-23/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-556639\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-23-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Minimalist room with wooden floors and walls, featuring a simple desk, chair, and a frosted glass door. A soft light illuminates the space, creating a serene atmosphere.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-23-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-23-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-23-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-23-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-23.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/the-boundless-residence-merges-natures-with-modern-living-spaces/boundess-residence-guangdong-china-lake-cdd-24/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-556640\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-24-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"Modern bathroom with marble walls, a large mirror above a wooden vanity, and a white freestanding bathtub near a window with blinds.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-24-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-24-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-24-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-24-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-24.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eGreen Island Lake is renowned for its rich biodiversity and scenic beauty. Surrounded by towering camphor, maple, and banyan trees, and centered around a “heart-shaped island” that serves as a sanctuary for rare herons, the location evokes a sense of peace and rejuvenation. At dawn and dusk, the skies above the lake come alive with the graceful flight of thousands of herons, creating an awe-inspiring natural spectacle often described as a “paradise of birds.”\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/the-boundless-residence-merges-natures-with-modern-living-spaces/boundess-residence-guangdong-china-lake-cdd-25/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-556641\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-25-810x456.jpg\" alt=\"A serene cityscape featuring several high-rise buildings near a calm lake with lush green islands and a tree-lined shore under a clear blue sky.\" width=\"810\" height=\"456\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-25-810x456.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-25-800x450.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-25-768x432.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-25-600x337.jpg 600w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-25.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"attachment_556643\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/the-boundless-residence-merges-natures-with-modern-living-spaces/boundess-residence-guangdong-china-lake-cdd-27-he-xiaoping-li-xinglin/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-556643\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-27-He-Xiaoping-Li-Xinglin-810x648.jpg\" alt=\"A black and white photo of two individuals with neutral expressions standing against a textured wall. The person on the left wears glasses and a white shirt; the one on the right wears glasses and a dark shirt.\" width=\"810\" height=\"648\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-27-He-Xiaoping-Li-Xinglin-810x648.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-27-He-Xiaoping-Li-Xinglin-800x640.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-27-He-Xiaoping-Li-Xinglin-768x614.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Boundess-Residence-Guangdong-China-Lake-cdd-27-He-Xiaoping-Li-Xinglin.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eHe Xiaoping and Li Xinglin of c.dd\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTo see more projects by c.dd, click \u003ca href=\"https://www.archilovers.com/teams/635450/c-dd.html#projects\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003ehere\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003ePhotography by Jack Qin.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2021/11/Caroline-Williamson-100x100.jpg\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2021/11/Caroline-Williamson.jpg 2x\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" alt=\"\"/\u003e \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eC